node.text:
HELLO so uh this is kinda crappy but I’m just gonna post it anyway because I barely post things when I’m sad or anything but the truth is, i’ve been not :) feeling :) the greatest :) for the past month and I just wanted to document this along with thanking you guys for the support u give me. i’m doing a lot better now btw. this song means a lot to me and i’d like to share it. hope y’all enjoy my cover of All I Want by Kodaline @ 1am. 
thankyou guys.

node.text:
When life gets tough, remember that YOU always got your back🪴 you are the person who is always going to be with you. So Treat yourself with love and kindness. You are your own lover for life ❤️ I will always be here for you as well ;) I love you 🥰 now go look in the mirror and give urself a kiss it’s Leo szn 😝 let’s make the comment section as positive as we can!!! We all need it 🥢
-
Also the songs are by my bestie @danakadan and they bring me great peace
